{"tid":1710870,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中大情況極之嚴竣, 三大出口封左兩個, 打死人都沒人知啊！","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:16:58.000Z","uid":167548,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"38a9db44214a7ab62f05595c55b4d76fa8b5450b","tid":1710870,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終於明白點解琴日暴大支那生趕著走！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n駐守暴大嘅戰略意義是咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710570</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#119Portra400&bull;29 分鐘前</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係人呀屌你</strong><br />\n入面個個都係手足<br />\n而家三個門口封左兩個<br />\n成個山頭咁大比狗入到去打死人冇人知</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#51ajheyt&bull;45 分鐘前<br />\n中大可能無戰略意義但大學作為民運嘅發源地同中心<br />\n呢個咁有象徵意義嘅地方<br />\n係咪比人打但守都唔守就退<br />\n我都好驚手足比人拉比人打<br />\n但可以退去邊？我地已經退得太多<br />\n今日學校 聽日踩入屋企<br />\n最後係咪逼到去懸崖 話守嚟無謂跳落去就算<br />\n今日一退 下次只會再退三退</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60我可以忘記你&bull;43 分鐘前<br />\n好心你啦 兄弟、正義 大過你D所謂戰略意義下嘛?<br />\n下下講戰略 郁D就賣一批兄弟出去 邊個仲會陪你撐落去啊?<br />\n你同777有咩分別啊用咁既思維諗野<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ks3f7ud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fks3f7ud.jpg&h=2e091943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQo0y9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQo0y9s.jpg&h=b3701fa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11ce6331b51d66eb22ad69f2f5a429af2cc6c99d","tid":1710870,"uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"聽日吐露港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b7b3419aec6d770f1